{"tid":2028604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「認同幫我推出去」大家請初選投票，成立自己嘅國民議會","createTime":"2020-05-22T01:50:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T08:54:49.000Z","uid":42007,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d1b60ac5c5ff8d59a6fd129dab4abfcf07a36fc0","tid":2028604,"uid":42007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T01:50:10.000Z","msg":"政治一日都太長<br />\n<br />\n當初，初選目的為增加民主派入立法會嘅機會，從而達致35+攬炒。但係喺郭榮鏗內會被DQ，到尋日中國想繞過香港立會立港安法，一切一切，都顯示出立會35+嘅可能，越來越微。<br />\n<br />\n大家係時候要換下手段。<br />\n<br />\n要知道35+係手段，係光復香港嘅手段。手段可以變，但目的唔會變。<br />\n<br />\n喺立會越來越冇用嘅情況下，大家可以照試35+，但初選嘅目的，就唔會再只係為35+服務，而係邁向國民議會嘅過程。<br />\n<br />\n試諗下，一個獨派係初選當選，但被DQ，佢可以全心全意去海外遊說，佢可以全心全意成立海外軍隊。<br />\n<br />\n換言之，初選，係公投，係香港人真正選擇自己代表嘅時候。<br />\n<br />\n你想代表香港嘅，係泛民，定係素人？<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候，我希望眾候選人，可以喺初選真正打開天窗說亮話，敢於俾人知你係獨派。<br />\n<br />\n至於9月立會？由plan b做囉"},{"pid":"ad8fe8a3aab0ab03b2787089fcbce00cd597c4af","tid":2028604,"uid":42007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T01:50:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9690bec68295c710e51ae87f1bab57864f8da865","tid":2028604,"uid":42007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T01:50:42.000Z","msg":"認同請推"},{"pid":"33569c79425520df04fee044e1fa11393ea3e4d3","tid":2028604,"uid":42007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T01:51:06.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"c443080cd741b6282a932b40a346db78ee7080a2","tid":2028604,"uid":42007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T01:51:17.000Z","msg":"有冇人幫手推？"},{"pid":"9d7299c4d2222dcad7d3fe2dd04e9b4543c81656","tid":2028604,"uid":42007,"lik